title: The Bakery & Cafe at Rose Cottage
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Stocks Earth Balance butter (vegan), almond milk for coffee drinks, has fresh bread and vegan cookies. Occasionally offers vegan soups and house-made seitan. Owner knows what vegan means, so if there's no vegan soup on the day you go, the the kitchen will custom make something for you.
